    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Long rakes for gathering together mown hay and other similar material into windrows ready for pitching; may be hand-held or mounted and pulled by an animal or tractor.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
